You can only play 1 on 1 on the map.

Each player has 20 weapons on their side. 2 awp, 2 scout and 12 grenades in the middle of the map, whoever takes them will be stronger than his opponent.

The map looks similar to the standard well-known Cbble map, but only its mini version.Â Good luck having fun with your friend on this wonderful and wonderful map!
